Forty years later, it is now available in a splendid collection of men's and women's timepieces in steel, pink gold, white gold or two-tone versions, to accompany the most active of lifestyles. Self-winding mechanical movement. Caliber 324 s c. Date window. Centre seconds hand. Silvered white dial, gold applied hour markers with luminescent coating. ABOUT


This pre-owned, 2010 Omega Seamaster Diver 300M 213.30.42.40.01.001 is in like new condition. The watch comes with a red Omega travel box, along with Omega international warranty card, Pictograms card and Chronometer Certificate card. The watch also comes with additional 1 year warranty from us.




All of our watches undergo a thorough inspection of accuracy, functionality and condition to meet our strict standards. Additionally, we check each watch against records to ensure authenticity and ownership status.




This classic Seamaster features an iconic wave patterned dial in black, with added chronometer and quick change date complications. The dial is surrounded by a 41.5mm stainless steel case that is home to a black aluminium bezel insert, fitted with unidirectional diving scale. The watch is then presented on a stainless steel bracelet in alternating polished and steel finishes and is powered by the Omega Calibre 1164 automatic movement.
